lead_paragraph: Britain qualified fastest on Friday in the men's 4x100 meters medley relay, threatening to spoil the party for Michael Phelps when he swims the last race of his epic Olympic career on Saturday.

headline.main: Swimming: Britain Fastest Through to Relay Final, Phelps' Last Race
